@@TJvRadioGroup
<TITLEIMG TJvRadioGroup>
#JVCLInfo
<GROUP JVCL.CommCtrl,JVCL.Buttons.Radio>
<FLAG Component>
Summary
  A radio group with enhancements.
Description
  Use TJvRadioGroup when you need a radio group with some extended capabilities. TJvRadioGroup
  derives from TRadioGroup but adds the following enhancements: CaptionVisible, HintColor,
  EdgeBorders,
  EdgeInner, EdgeOuter, ReadOnly, OnMouseEnter, OnMouseLeave, OnItemHint and OnParentColorChanged.

